text: Aluis Kuylaars (born 17 May 1971) is an international cricketer who made 23 One Day International appearances for South Africa national women's cricket team between 1997 and 2000. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Cricketers from Cape Town Category:South African women cricketers Category:South Africa women One Day International cricketers
